data.description: Price reduction!  Best investment available. 2 bedroom, 2 bath villa in 55+, pet friendly community of  Springwood Villas II. This home has tons of natural light, large living room, dining room, eat in space in the kitchen, and Florida room.  Rear patio surrounded by mature landscaping provides private space for outdoor entertaining.  Washer, dryer hookups and laundry sink are located in the garage, which not only has room for your car but also has tons of storage space.  The community amenities include a clubhouse, heated pool, library, auditorium, game room w/pool tables & bingo, shuffleboard & workout room with updated equipment and the HOA fee includes cable, internet, building exterior and lawn mowing, water, sewer and trash pick-up.  Conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, entertainment and recreations and just a short drive to I-275, airports, St Petersburg, Tampa, and beautiful gulf beaches.
